## Stripe Connect

Stripe Connect functionality is built in Voxel functionality that lets users onboard as a vendor, and start selling any product types you make available and get paid instantly or periodically, while your platform collects commissions.

It can be enabled under **Ecommerce > Configure Stripe > Stripe Connect**

Learn more about Connect

[https://stripe.com/connect](https://stripe.com/connect)

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### Charge types

There are two types of charges available when enabling Marketplace functionality in Voxel:

- Destination charges
- Separate charges and transfers

[Learn more about charge types](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_destination-separate-charges-marketplace_.md)

### Vendor fees

You can easily create fees about products sold through your site and apply them conditionally based on role, plan or user ID.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Onboarding flow for vendors

Vendor onboarding is done through the **Stripe Account (VX)** widget which can be placed in WP-admin > **Design > General > Orders > Stripe Connect** template

![](data:image/png;base64,)![](data:image/png;base64,)

_A preview of vendor onboarding wizard_

### Where to enable and configure Connect

Connect can be enabled and setup in your Stripe account dashboard

[https://dashboard.stripe.com/connect/set-up](https://dashboard.stripe.com/connect/set-up)

During onboarding process, some of the question are related to the type of integration that is available in Voxel:

#### How will funds flow on your platform

Buyers will purchase from you

Sell to buyers yourself and send payouts.

- Buyers will purchase goods and services directly from you
- Pay out some or all of what you collect to sellers
- Your platform will appear on receipts
- Youll be responsible for refunds and disputes
- Youll be liable if sellers cant pay back negative balances
- Youll be able to support sellers in the European Union, United Kingdom, and Gibraltar

#### How will sellers be paid out?

Sellers will be paid out individually

Collect a payment from a buyer and send a payout to an individual seller.

- Pay out a single seller per payment
- Pay out some or all of the funds you collect

#### Where will sellers create their account?

Onboarding hosted by Stripe

Redirect sellers to an onboarding experience built and hosted by Stripe.

- Customise with your brand colours and logo
- Stripe will determine and collect KYC requirements for payments
- Automatically supports the European Union countries, United Kingdom, Gibraltar, and 37 languages

#### Where will sellers manage their account?

Express Dashboard

Redirect sellers to a lightweight and customisable dashboard built and hosted by Stripe.

- Customise with your brand colours and logo
- Sellers can track balances, payouts, and earnings in real time
- Sellers can update their bank accounts and personal details
- Automatically supports the European Union, United Kingdom, Gibraltar, and 37 languages
